{"tid":1559011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個雖然唔係識咗好耐 但感情幾好嘅朋友","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:43:02.000Z","uid":74622,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d64543dbf98a2b084379ebdf17983893ab0b13b5","tid":1559011,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"我自問我自己嘅性格好難去識朋友<br />\n而我都好慶幸我識到哩位朋友<br />\n但自從佢講完一句嘢之後我就唔能夠當佢係朋友<br />\n佢係由反送中之前就咁啱入咗學堂去做狗<br />\n都仲Train緊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 其實你嘅政治立場係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我入咗學堂之後，的確係撐警多啲嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔係因為畀人洗咗腦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 係由兩方面角度分析，的確警方都有好多錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 示威者咁耐以嚟都係破壞死物，最嚴重都係沙田新城市咬斷指，況且係黑警挖眼先。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 每個國家示威警察都要執法，一定會有衝突。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 執法還執法，有晒指引去畀你哋遵守，執法要出示委任證，唔出示當佢Cosplay? 再者，有指引講明開任何槍都只可以對下半身，點解要射眼?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 其實開真槍唔係打機 = =<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好難瞄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我見到真係屌你老母<br />\n仲虧你自己講得出兩個角度去分析<br />\n女First Aid 係尖沙咀狗屋出面個巴士站就要畀你哋啲狗開槍射眼?<br />\n難瞄咪即係你哋訓練唔夠<br />\n解散警隊啦仆街<br />\n希望你第時子女出世唔會少咁隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">612 721 805 831 新屋嶺 追究到底<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"10ede79c3a3ac34ef124d06b55e9c9b06a7173a0","tid":1559011,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c403016292831ab6dc32ac203600515badaba1","tid":1559011,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30285554cb0bb0e7232f225fd0b3ff63dd06ac2","tid":1559011,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"係狗就已經要絕交啦<br />\n同狗有關係嘅人都要全面杯葛"},{"pid":"5ab60fa7edb88300e55afa4d42fd9a1ddea9def4","tid":1559011,"uid":74622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e30285554cb0bb0e7232f225fd0b3ff63dd06ac2","tid":1559011,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"係狗就已經要絕交啦<br />\n同狗有關係嘅人都要全面杯葛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"原本諗住佢有得救 我諗太多"},{"pid":"3193625a08c0ea92a06dbab36449554afc3e9a47","tid":1559011,"uid":273803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"絕交啦，記得 back up 晒佢所有個人資料上老豆搵仔"},{"pid":"033ad5a5a08feb047d35ee1102f3a43d472f83cc","tid":1559011,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3193625a08c0ea92a06dbab36449554afc3e9a47","tid":1559011,"uid":273803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"絕交啦，記得 back up 晒佢所有個人資料上老豆搵仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ec02b4751e702576f1f09da310eeb30c845a76","tid":1559011,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r